ompendium[wfrp4e-core.skills.XQiiwS9m2Du1IMUz]{Language (Any)}, @Compendium[wfrp4e-core.skills.DRO5DLF6UcfkvNSh]{Lore (Any)}<br /><strong>Talents</strong>: @Compendium[wfrp4e-core.talents.mqo51ORnxijcqNNu]{Frightening}, @Compendium[wfrp4e-core.talents.E98mVLZgE8bX5vQW]{Hatred (Undead)}, @Compendium[wfrp4e-core.talents.mgeiaDZXei7JBEgo]{Iron Will}, @Compendium[wfrp4e-core.talents.F2EiuAc6IpaGd4J7]{War Wizard}<br /><strong>Trappings</strong>: Ghastly Lectern, Library (Magic)<br /><br /></p>","img":"modules/wfrp4e-core/art/careers/amethyst-wizard.webp"}
